Action Capy surface <code>sendkeys</code> <code>sendkeys "selector" keys "{{text}}"</code> <code>action(click)</code> <code>click "selector"</code> <code>action(double-click)</code> <code>double-click "selector"</code> <code>scroll-until-stable</code> <code>scroll-until-stable "body" down stable 800ms max 20</code> <p>Library implementation pattern:</p> <pre><code>function click
    arg literal "click"
    arg capture selector string
    append context.flow {
        run: "action",
        params: { action: "click", selector: selector }
    }
end
</code></pre>
